                <Paragraphs>
                  <Paragraph>
                    <TextRuns>
                      <TextRun>
                        <Value>The animal ingredient(s) in this shipment contain(s) mechanically de-boned beef made from neck bones and brisket bones sourced from facilities where the materials have received the FSIS mark of inspection under an AMS EV program and/or under an APHIS EU or Canada approval.  The ingredient(s) do not contain and have not been contaminated with the skull (including brain), trigeminal ganglia, eyes, spinal cord, dorsal root ganglia, and vertebral column (excluding vertebrae of the tail, transverse processes of thoracic and lumbar vertebrae, and wings of the sacrum) from bovines aged 30 months and older; and distal ileum of small intestine (last 80cm or 200in of small intestine) and tonsils from bovines of all ages.</Value>
                        <Style />
                      </TextRun>
                    </TextRuns>
                    <Style />
                  </Paragraph>
                </Paragraphs>
