                        <Value>We hereby certify that these goods were produced in compliance with all applicable requirements of the Fair Labor Standards Act, as amended, including but not limited to sections 6, 7, 12, and 15, and of regulations and orders of the United States Department of Labor.  Among other things, the Fair Labor Standards Act (1) prohibits the use of oppressive child labor in commerce, in the production of goods for commerce, or in any enterprise engaged in commerce or in the production of goods for commerce, and (2) restricts the shipment of delivery of goods produced in an establishment in which oppressive child labor has been employed.</Value>
